00:10:33.310 --> 00:10:36.110
BRETT LEONARD: PopFictionLife
itself, yes.

00:10:36.110 --> 00:10:39.300
But we're going to be expanding
the genre to

00:10:39.300 --> 00:10:42.400
incorporate other kinds
of subject matter.

00:10:42.400 --> 00:10:44.940
But I always probably will want
to incorporate music,

00:10:44.940 --> 00:10:48.460
because you wouldn't necessarily
always have to

00:10:48.460 --> 00:10:51.620
