00:10:56.930 --> 00:10:58.020
We had a lot of fun doing it.

00:10:58.020 --> 00:11:04.230
So it was an opportunity to do
something that can combine.

00:11:04.230 --> 00:11:06.430
Those things came together
just perfectly.

