00:39:13.350 --> 00:39:16.340
themselves greater than
most actors do in

00:39:16.340 --> 00:39:17.180
a traditional film.

00:39:17.180 --> 00:39:20.890
So there's a real frision
that takes place there.

00:39:20.890 --> 00:39:22.030
And I think that's unique.

00:39:22.030 --> 00:39:25.240
I think that authenticity is
something people can find and

00:39:25.240 --> 00:39:26.430
respond to.

00:39:26.430 --> 00:39:27.050
FEMALE SPEAKER: I agree.

00:39:27.050 --> 00:39:28.600
I think this whole concept
